### using DifferentialEquations
using Plots


n=0
# Parmetros como vector
p = [0.4, 0.5, 0.1, 0.1, 0.5]  # A, , , , 

"""Neoclassical Production Function"""
function F(x, p::Vector)
    A, , , _, _ = p
    return (A * x^ - (n+) * x)
end

"""The Ramsey-Cass-Koompans system"""
function ramsey!(du, u, p::Vector, t)
    # Parmetros del vector
    A, , , ,  = p

    # Variables
    K, C = u

    # Sistema ODE, donde
    #K'=F(k)- K - C
    
    du[1] = -(A * K^ - (+n) * K - C)
    du[2] = -( * A * K^( - 1) -() - ) * () * C

    nothing
end

"""Calcular el estado estacionario"""
function ss(p::Vector)
    # Parmetros del vector
    A, , , , _ = p

    # Estado estacionario
    Kss = ( * A / ( + ))^(1 / (1 - ))
    Css = A * Kss^ - () * Kss

    return Kss, Css
end

# Estado estacionario
Kss, Css = ss(p)

# Ejecutar "hacia atrs" | iniciar por debajo del estado estacionario
tspan = (0.0, 50)
tweak = 0.98
u0 = [0.999999 * Kss; 0.999999 * tweak * Css]
ode = ODEProblem(ramsey!, u0, tspan, p)
sol1 = DifferentialEquations.solve(ode, abstol=1e-8, reltol=1e-8)

# Funcin de poltica C = (K)
plt = plot(
    title="Funciones en Modelo Ramsey-Cass-Koopmans",
    xlims=(0, 2 * Kss),
    ylims=(0, 2 * Css),
    xlabel="K(t)",
    ylabel="C(t)",
    legend=false
)

# Dibujar nullclines
plot!(plt, x -> F(x, p), 0, 2, color=:"#6E9DE2"  , linewidth=3, legend=false)
vline!(plt, [Kss], color=:black, linewidth=1,linestyle=:dash, legend=false)

plot!(plt, sol1, xflip=false, vars=(1, 2), xlims=(0, 2 * Kss), ylims=(0, 2 * Css), color=:"#E36173", linewidth=3)

# Ejecutar "hacia atrs" | iniciar por encima del estado estacionario
tspan = (0, 100.0)
tweak = 1.01
u0 = [1.00001 * Kss; 1.00001 * tweak * Css]
ode = ODEProblem(ramsey!, u0, tspan, p)
sol2 = DifferentialEquations.solve(ode, abstol=1e-8, reltol=1e-8)
plot!(plt, sol2, xflip=false, vars=(1, 2), xlims=(0, 2 * Kss), ylims=(0, 2 * Css), color=:"#E36173", linewidth=3)

# Estetica grafico :  
scatter!((1.0, 0.3), label=["Stationary State" "."], color=:"#6D7273")

#savefig(plt, "ramsey-stable-arm.png")

using CairoMakie
p = [0.4, 0.5, 0.1, 0.1, 0.5]  # A, , , , 

"""Ramsey model equations as points in (K,C) space"""
function ramseyEq(K, C, p)
    A, , , ,  = p[1], p[2], p[3], p[4], p[5]

    dK = -(A * K^ - (+n) * K - C)
    dC = -( * A * K^( - 1) -() - ) *  * C
    return Point(dK, dC)
end

let
    fig = Figure(fontsize = 25)
    ax = Axis(fig, xlabel="k(t)", ylabel="c(t)", title="Diagrama de Fase Modelo Ramsey", backgroundcolor = :black)
    streamplot!(ax, (x,y)->ramseyEq(x,y,p), 0..2*Kss, 0..2*Css, colormap = Reverse(:plasma),
        gridsize= (32,32), arrow_size = 10)
    fig[1, 1] = ax
    display(fig)
    save("ramsey-streamplot.png", fig)
end
